{"id":22,"date":"2023-03-10T01:21:31","date_gmt":"2023-03-10T01:21:31","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/localhost\/BSU-Open%20University\/?page_id=22"},"modified":"2023-06-23T08:28:11","modified_gmt":"2023-06-23T00:28:11","slug":"admission-requirements","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"http:\/\/localhost\/bsu-open%20university\/index.php\/admission-requirements\/","title":{"rendered":"Admission"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Applicants will be notified on the result of application through email. If no email has been received, this means that the application is still on process.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:45px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><strong><a href=\"#submit-deadlines\">Deadlines of submission. (S.Y 2023-2024)<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-4\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:100%\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-constrained\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table is-style-stripes\"><table><thead><tr><th><strong>For Initial Evaluation<\/strong><\/th><\/tr><\/thead><tbody><tr><td>1.<strong> <a href=\"http:\/\/localhost\/bsu-open%20university\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/OU-Form-1-Application-for-Admission-1.pdf\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"http:\/\/localhost\/bsu-open%20university\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/OU-Form-1-Application-for-Admission-1.pdf\">OU Form 1 Admission Form<\/a><\/strong><\/td><\/tr><tr><td>2. One (1) recommendation letter from your former professors\/supervisor. <strong><a href=\"http:\/\/localhost\/bsu-open%20university\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/OU-Form-2-Recommendation-Form-1.pdf\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"http:\/\/localhost\/bsu-open%20university\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/OU-Form-2-Recommendation-Form-1.pdf\">OU Form 2 Recommendation Form<\/a><\/strong><\/td><\/tr><tr><td>3. Permit to study from head of your agency if employed. <strong><a href=\"http:\/\/localhost\/bsu-open%20university\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/OU-Form-3-Permit-to-Study-1.pdf\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"http:\/\/localhost\/bsu-open%20university\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/OU-Form-3-Permit-to-Study-1.pdf\">OU Form 3 Permit to Study<\/a><\/strong><\/td><\/tr><tr><td>4. Official Transcript of Records and Transcript of Records (OTR\/TOR)<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>5. Payment of Application Fee of \u20b1100 for Local and \u20b11,500 for foreign nationals (Non-refundable).<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>6. An essay of about 300 words indicating your purpose for applying to the distance education program and your plan after completing the degree.<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>7. &nbsp;Latest identical ID picture (2\u201d x 2\u201d) with plain white background.<\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table is-style-stripes\"><table><thead><tr><th><strong>Additional Requirement for Qualified Applicants<\/strong><\/th><\/tr><\/thead><tbody><tr><td>1. Original Certificate of Transfer Credential\/ Honorable Dismissal from the last school attended (not required for BSU graduates).<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>2. Two (2) photocopy of PSA birth certificate and marriage certificate (for married)<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>3. Valid visa for foreign nationals. (Foreign student only)<\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:41px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-vivid-purple-color has-text-color has-medium-font-size\"><strong>Submit Documents to our office via Courier or in person<\/strong>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-constrained\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p><strong>CONTACT INFORMATION<\/strong><br><strong>The Director<\/strong><br>Open University<br>Benguet State University<br>Km. 5, Balili, La Trinidad, Benguet 2601 PH<br>(+63) 915-152-8703<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-constrained\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-6\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:100%\">\n<figure id=\"submit-deadlines\" class=\"wp-block-table is-style-stripes\"><table><thead><tr><th class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\"><strong>Deadlines of submission.<\/strong> (<strong>S.Y 2023-2024<\/strong>)<\/th><\/tr><\/thead><tbody><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\"><strong>1st Semester<\/strong> <br><strong>Admission Deadline:<\/strong> June 30, 2023<br><strong>Enrollment:&nbsp;<\/strong>JULY 24-AUGUST 5, 2023&nbsp;&nbsp;<br><strong>Class Start:<\/strong>&nbsp;August 7&nbsp; &#8211; December 9, 2023<\/td><\/tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\"><strong>2nd Semester<\/strong> <br>Admission Deadline: Nov. 29, 2023<br><strong>Enrollment:<\/strong>&nbsp;JANUARY 3-6, 2024&nbsp;<br><strong>Class Start:&nbsp;<\/strong>January 8 &#8211; May 11, 2024<\/td><\/tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\"><strong>MID-TERM YEAR<\/strong> <br>Admission Deadline: April 26, 2023<br><strong>Enrollment:&nbsp;<\/strong>MAY 27-JUNE 1, 2024&nbsp;&nbsp;<br><strong>Class Start:<\/strong>&nbsp;June 3 -July 12, 2024<\/td><\/tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\"><\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:51px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-horizontal is-content-justification-left is-layout-flex wp-container-8\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost\/BSU-Open%20University\/index.php\/contact-us\/\">Contact Us<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Applicants